{"tid":950224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗年近九旬翁　YOHO Midtown墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-12-21T11:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T16:36:04.000Z","uid":20058,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1ef43ef4e7bc405daae681c5a3e36782f0827a","tid":950224,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T11:01:29.000Z","msg":"元朗元龍街9號YOHO Midtown發生男子墮樓死亡事件，今日(21日)下午約1時，一名保安員在上址巡邏期間，發現一名男子倒臥在平台昏迷，懷疑他從高處墮下，慌忙報警。救護員接報到場，證實該男子已傷重死亡。 <br />\n<br />\n警方調查證實死者姓鄧(87歲)，相信從上址一單位墮下，事件無可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。據悉，鄧翁近日受生活問題困擾，致情緒低落，不排除因此而萌生死念。 <br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n利民會： 3512 2626 <br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=g%2BOCMfozvJQoZ9Bmm2ntXZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=47e51f30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181221/mobile/bkn-20181221131823235-1221_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181221%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181221131823235-1221_00822_001.html&d=g%2BOCMfozvJQoZ9Bmm2ntXZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=b0b8e382\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181221/mobile/bkn-20181221131823235-1221_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"62be882cff0d7c3c6c807b915ce6aee2729e5056","tid":950224,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T11:06:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2471351f258b9a1d5de1ef144e5d7ea7c0ddda8","tid":950224,"uid":23423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T11:07:12.000Z","msg":"跌！"},{"pid":"4428843011848c3a0b3f94277a6bf80ecaea4d99","tid":950224,"uid":108467,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T11:08:10.0